      "content": "i mean i know i should talk to my doctor but i'm just looking for some info first. i've read online that garlic is a natural blood thinner. if i just started taking a really high dose of concentrated garlic extract, wouldn't that basically do the same thing as the warfarin without the side effects? like, how much would i need to take to actually see an effect?",
